{"tid":1886802,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[創意台] 青沙公路致命交通意外 「死傷者」散落一地","createTime":"2020-02-19T06:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T11:17:54.000Z","uid":164435,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"09fdef7bebbd9da0d51385d747bad4c7b0b35f52","tid":1886802,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6137G8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6137G8.jpg&h=3cdcf885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有鮮魚跌在車轆底。詹家志攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdBPiOT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdBPiOT.jpg&h=7d237f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaaDWAB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaaDWAB.jpg&h=098c171c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早上9時半，青沙公路葵涌段往沙田方向有3車相撞。一輛雙層巴士、一輛運魚車及一輛拖車相撞，其中巴士車頭損毀，車長受傷，由救護車送瑪嘉烈醫院。由於運魚車車斗被撞凹，猛烈撞擊下運載的鮮魚都飛墮地上，估計有40至50條，部份還紮紮跳，司機連忙逐一撿起。警方到場封鎖部份行車線，現場交通受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200219/GQXYCULWTNJ66BZMJ5LBDPU7O4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200219%2FGQXYCULWTNJ66BZMJ5LBDPU7O4%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=d617c49b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200219%2FGQXYCULWTNJ66BZMJ5LBDPU7O4%2F&h=ca0debdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200219/GQXYCULWTNJ66BZMJ5LBDPU7O4/</a>"},{"pid":"fb0d5397ed663d5d5f3dbae319549d26d54f7cfe","tid":1886802,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1e95dc2fcc191d6db2ed0ff2738bb253703353","tid":1886802,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"RIP魚魚\\